Cyberpunk style digital illustration of a futuristic data exchange hub: glowing streams of structured JSON-like data packets flowing through neon-lit conduits between a massive dark monolithic database tower and sleek floating holographic interface panels. The scene shows intricate circuit-board patterns embedded in wet rain-slicked streets below, with purple and cyan light reflecting off metallic surfaces. Data streams appear as organized geometric shapes—brackets, curly braces, and nested structures—traveling through translucent tubes that pulse with electric blue energy. A lone figure in a long coat observes the data flow from a elevated platform, silhouetted against the glow of massive server racks stretching into a hazy, neon-drenched sky. Atmospheric fog drifts between towering tech structures, creating depth and mystery.
